														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-460019">
									

<p>At first, I thought, "Good grief, it's a <a href="http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LighterAndSofter">Lighter And Softer</a> knock-off of <a href="/scp-173">SCP-173</a> and <a href="/scp-689">SCP-689</a>."</p>
<p>But when I finished, I thought, "Huh. In spite of the massive similarities … somehow this one <em>works</em> for me."</p>
<p>I guess the non-lethal nature of this one, ironically, makes it scarier. If 173 or 689 catch you, you'll be dead before it ever occurs to you to be afraid. This one? You're walking along, for some reason you turn around, an-OHHOLYSHITITSRIGHTBEHINDYOU! My little brother and I used to try to do things like that to each other all the time, usually by hiding in the bathroom, just next to the door.</p>

							</div>

								
					
